":"e47b738f125b021d5926d1995f57f3fa0a4e18fc","tid":2431674,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f0f790f9b799f0adcf8fbf2a1d59c9a4cb51a37f","tid":2431674,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0d9d34f00b71ffa0a353ff85d36f481fadec10d","tid":2431674,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:26:26.000Z","msg":"粒線體(Mitochondria)同細胞質(Cytoplasm)會一齊分Citrate？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"唔太明依句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:52:09.000Z","msg":"即係身體入面嘅Citrate會平均分配比粒線體同細胞質？定係有咩機制？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afca750d55e9e73ca3db2904ec6e13ec2e6395e","tid":2431674,"uid":114091,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:52:42.000Z","msg":"唔係唔岩, 但係實際上你要食幾多PROTEIN先會超過maintenance calories, 好多時D野唔係淨講理論<br />\n<br />\n同埋駛乜咁多道理呀, 好簡單就係energy intake vs energy output搞掂啦"},{"pid":"d5f2622b92667f7bf24a7e84a4d01c3cab82ee41","tid":2431674,"uid":114091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:54:01.000Z","msg":"調返轉講你每日如果食唔夠maintenance calories, 只食carbs都唔會肥, 不過同時冇muscle mass咁解"},{"pid":"e38a60bc32e19dce1917264c6f3e5a2dba8d9602","tid":2431674,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e47b738f125b021d5926d1995f57f3fa0a4e18fc","tid":2431674,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f0f790f9b799f0adcf8fbf2a1d59c9a4cb51a37f","tid":2431674,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0d9d34f00b71ffa0a353ff85d36f481fadec10d","tid":2431674,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:26:26.000Z","msg":"粒線體(Mitochondria)同細胞質(Cytoplasm)會一齊分Citrate？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"唔太明依句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:52:09.000Z","msg":"即係身體入面嘅Citrate會平均分配比粒線體同細胞質？定係有咩機制？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:56:19.000Z","msg":"有機制控制，cytoplasm從mito攞citrate的話，要拋返其他野(pyruvate)入去mito以作交換。"},{"pid":"abd7125fa2bb39ea176d42f9fecc52cecbdaaed6","tid":2431674,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a71f5db2f9685cc594d8321c20d970c4de9d84f","tid":2431674,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"借個位問下可唔可整一集講corticosteroids<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解搽皮膚又得 醫哮喘又得 乜都得咁勁<br />\n<br />\n其他萬用藥例如antihistamines 都只能做抗敏藥 冇corticosteroids咁神"}]}